What is the Global Citizen Festival and has it contributed to reducing poverty in any way?
Next Saturday, the Global Citizen Festival will take place in New York City, an annual music event that boasts an incredibly impressive line-up of performing stars and an equally impressive mission – eradicating poverty in the world.
